body_html:
This seems to say it is 5, so whatever you were looking at probably had a mistake.
http://www.nvidia.com/object/quadro-for-mobile-workstations.html
In any case, we just trust what the nvidia api returns, so this is not a TensorFlow issue for sure. Hopefully 5.0 is sufficient for your needs. Closing for now, Thanks! I am also told that the compute capacity really has minimal performance impact, certainly 5.2 to 5.0 hasn't made a different in our testing.
